  "body": "#### System information\n\nGeth version: 1.5.0-unstable-ab664c7e\nOS & Version: Windows/Linux/OSX\n#### Expected behaviour\n\nThe JSON-RPC api suggests that it should be possible to set up a filter for logs in pending transactions using `pending` for `toBlock`: \nhttps://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JSON-RPC#eth_newfilter\n#### Actual behaviour\n\nOnly logs in confirmed transactions can be found.\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\nBroadcast a transaction that creates a log. Keep searching for the log with toBlock: pending. It will only appear when the transaction is confirmed.\n",
